==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: glowing
<hw>glowing</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>softly bright or
radiant.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> aglow(predicate), lambent, luminous,
lucent.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>highly enthusiastic; <as>as, <ex>glowing</ex>
praise</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>brilliantly colored and apparently giving off
light.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fluorescent.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>afire; <as>as, <ex>glowing</ex> embers</as>.</def>
<mark>[prenominal]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> burning.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glowingly</ent>⟦br⟧
